text: DXPH (98.9 FM), broadcasting as 98.9 Mystical FM, is a radio station in the Philippines owned and operated by the Government of Dinagat Islands through its Provincial Information Office. The station's studio and transmitter are located at the Annex Bldg., Provincial Capitol, Brgy. Cuarenta, San Jose, Dinagat Islands. It serves as a community radio station of Dinagat Islands.LGU Dinagat Islands launches community-based broadcasting systemDOLE Caraga-PDI goes on-airCaraga In Focus. p.3 ==References== Category:Radio stations established in 2019
